00:19:04,570 --> 00:19:05,950
If Demon Realm has any unusual action,


271
00:19:06,310 --> 00:19:07,240
fight fiercely with them.


272
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,040
Yes.


273
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,510
Your Majesty,


274
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:11,200
in the war between the Heaven and the Demon ,


275
00:19:11,420 --> 00:19:15,280
every Heavenly Emperor
will show up at battlefield


276
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:16,350
to enhance troop morale.


277
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:18,710
You just ascended the throne


278
00:19:18,710 --> 00:19:22,260
and you need to consolidate the power and position.


279
00:19:22,620 --> 00:19:26,000
If you can command troops in the frontline,


280
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,710
the heavenly generals and soldiers


281
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:31,680
will definitely be more loyal to Your Majesty.


282
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:32,750
I see.


283
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,170
You should be leaving.


284
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:35,460
Yes.


285
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,240
Kuang Lu,


286
00:19:41,860 --> 00:19:43,060
you should also be leaving.


287
00:19:43,460 --> 00:19:44,880
I need to think carefully


288
00:19:45,820 --> 00:19:47,640
how to deal with it.


289
00:19:49,280 --> 00:19:50,000
Yes.


290
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,370
Your Majesty.


291
00:20:04,710 --> 00:20:08,040
Water Immortal is anxiously
longing for Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir.


292
00:20:08,620 --> 00:20:10,260
It is God’s will whether she can get it or not.


293
00:20:11,020 --> 00:20:12,570
But as Leader Yin Que said,


294
00:20:13,420 --> 00:20:15,280
if Fire Immortal’s soul is still alive,


295
00:20:15,280 --> 00:20:16,750
with Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir,


296
00:20:17,370 --> 00:20:18,390
he might be reborn.


297
00:20:18,480 --> 00:20:19,060
Then…


298
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:22,710
I speak without thinking.


299
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:24,350
Please punish me.


300
00:20:26,260 --> 00:20:27,680
When did I ask you to kneel?


301
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,370
Stand up.


302
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,330
Thank you, Your Majesty.


303
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:47,910
Your Majesty.


304
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,150
What’s the matter?


305
00:20:50,220 --> 00:20:52,440
The dethroned Heavenly Empress
jumped off Linyuan Tower.


306
00:20:53,510 --> 00:20:54,170
Leave.


307
00:20:54,440 --> 00:20:55,150
And,


308
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:58,130
Water Immortal seems to be seriously injured


309
00:20:58,800 --> 00:20:59,910
and fainted just now.


310
00:21:18,970 --> 00:21:19,770
Why?


311
00:21:20,260 --> 00:21:21,770
I don’t know either.


312
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:23,370
The Light of Xuanqiong


313
00:21:23,820 --> 00:21:26,970
actually needs to be borne
by Water Immortal’s body.


314
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:28,970
Due to the strong light,


315
00:21:28,970 --> 00:21:30,840
I’m afraid her body has been melted.


316
00:21:31,110 --> 00:21:34,000
Even if you help her with magic power,


317
00:21:34,220 --> 00:21:38,220
I’m afraid she can only stay alive for some time.


318
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,770
You should be leaving.


319
00:21:44,260 --> 00:21:44,930
Yes.


320
00:22:11,150 --> 00:22:11,860
Mi,


321
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:15,110
I will find the way to save you.


322
00:22:53,540 --> 00:22:55,420
"Mengtuo Scripture"


323
00:22:58,130 --> 00:22:59,200
Blood Ball.


324
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,640
Change fate against God’s will.


325
00:23:28,930 --> 00:23:29,510
Mi,


326
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:32,570
since you are my inexorable doom,


327
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:34,530
now


328
00:23:36,220 --> 00:23:37,330
I come to accept it.


329
00:24:38,530 --> 00:24:39,460
Your Majesty,


330
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,530
what are you doing?


331
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:43,950
Leave!


332
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,420
Your Majesty,


333
00:24:46,220 --> 00:24:47,860
now the demon army is about to attack.


334
00:24:48,570 --> 00:24:49,640
If you hurt yourself,


335
00:24:49,860 --> 00:24:50,620
how can Heaven Realm...


336
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:54,260
how can Heaven Realm win them?


337
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:56,220
If I don’t save her now,


338
00:24:57,200 --> 00:24:58,620
it’ll be too late.


339
00:24:59,060 --> 00:24:59,910
Your Majesty!


340
00:24:59,910 --> 00:25:00,800
Leave!


341
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:41,020
Are you really going to
fight for King of Gu City?


342
00:25:41,550 --> 00:25:42,930
I’m not fighting for him,


343
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:44,800
but for Feng, for Demon Realm


344
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:45,910
and for this grudge.


345
00:25:46,310 --> 00:25:47,020
If it is for Demon Realm,


346
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:48,710
you should consider


347
00:25:48,930 --> 00:25:51,370
what consequences this war will bring.


348
00:25:51,950 --> 00:25:52,840
Your father is right.


349
00:25:53,150 --> 00:25:54,970
You really shouldn’t act on impulse


350
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:55,910
for Fire Immortal.


351
00:25:56,310 --> 00:25:57,730
But I have promised to fight this war,


352
00:25:58,130 --> 00:25:59,280
I can’t have cold feet.


353
00:25:59,730 --> 00:26:01,680
There can be no turning back now.


354
00:26:02,170 --> 00:26:02,880
Princess.


355
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:03,820
Stop.


356
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:04,880
Xu Feng died distressingly,


357
00:26:05,020 --> 00:26:06,260
and Heavenly Emperor is so arrogant.


358
00:26:06,620 --> 00:26:08,260
My father actually submits to humiliation.


359
00:26:09,060 --> 00:26:10,570
Though I don’t want to irritate him,


360
00:26:11,020 --> 00:26:13,370
I really can’t bear this.


361
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:16,400
If you are not willing to fight with me,


362
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:17,550
I won’t force you.


363
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:24,480
In fact, you know I don’t mean that.


364
00:26:24,660 --> 00:26:25,550
No matter what happens,


365
00:26:25,550 --> 00:26:27,460
I will share weal and woe with you.


366
00:26:58,930 --> 00:26:59,640
Your Majesty.


367
00:27:04,530 --> 00:27:05,330
I am fine.


368
00:27:17,060 --> 00:27:18,220
Your Majesty.


369
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:19,680
Did you use…


370
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:22,080
Do not let Jin Mi know this.


371
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:23,680
But…


372
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,600
This is a forbidden magic of Heaven Realm.


373
00:27:27,280 --> 00:27:28,400
I am Heavenly Emperor.


374
00:27:29,770 --> 00:27:31,550
If this matter is known by others,


375
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:33,280
I’m afraid there will be
changes in the six realms,


376
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:36,660
and Mi will be gossiped


377
00:27:38,080 --> 00:27:39,640
by others.


378
00:27:40,930 --> 00:27:41,860
Remember.


379
00:27:43,910 --> 00:27:46,170
Do not let others know this.


380
00:27:47,150 --> 00:27:47,910
Understand?


381
00:27:49,150 --> 00:27:50,310
I understand.


382
00:27:53,770 --> 00:27:54,440
Your Majesty.


383
00:27:57,060 --> 00:27:59,460
Drink this bowl of decoction
to nourish your body.


384
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:24,750
Phoenix.


385
00:28:26,530 --> 00:28:27,510
Phoenix.


386
00:28:28,350 --> 00:28:29,680
Phoenix.


387
00:28:36,170 --> 00:28:38,310
Water Immortal, you are awake.


388
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:41,600
Kuang Lu, what happened?


389
00:28:42,530 --> 00:28:43,120
Yesterday,


390
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:45,950
you injected the Light of
Xuanqiong into Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir.


391
00:28:46,750 --> 00:28:49,330
You were injured as
you couldn’t bear the strength


392
00:28:49,770 --> 00:28:50,570
of the Light of Xuanqiong.


393
00:28:51,730 --> 00:28:52,710
Luckily, His Majesty,


394
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:54,440
His Majesty


395
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:55,600
transferred some magic power to you


396
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:57,550
and thus saved you.


397
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,730
You can recover in a few days.


398
00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:02,350
His Majesty transferred
some magic power to me?


399
00:29:03,330 --> 00:29:04,440
How is he now?


400
00:29:05,510 --> 00:29:06,570
His Majesty is fine.


401
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,350
Just now immortals have things to report,


402
00:29:08,710 --> 00:29:10,310
so he is occupied now.


403
00:29:10,310 --> 00:29:11,770
He will come to see you some time later.


404
00:29:14,930 --> 00:29:16,040
Have a cup of tea.


405
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:17,860
Thanks.


406
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:20,260
Immortal,


407
00:29:22,170 --> 00:29:23,330
can you keep


408
00:29:24,620 --> 00:29:26,000
the next conversations


409
00:29:26,220 --> 00:29:27,330
between you and me?


410
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:30,800
Go ahead.


411
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:32,400
Is your heart


412
00:29:33,860 --> 00:29:35,060
made of ice?


413
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,220
Even if it is made of ice,


414
00:29:39,860 --> 00:29:43,200
as His Majesty paid for you time and time again,


415
00:29:43,730 --> 00:29:45,550
your heart should have melted.


416
00:29:49,820 --> 00:29:50,750
Immortal,


417
00:29:51,330 --> 00:29:52,480
I beg you.


418
00:29:52,750 --> 00:29:53,680
I beg you


419
00:29:53,950 --> 00:29:55,600
to show more feelings for His Majesty, OK?


420
00:29:56,220 --> 00:29:58,310
You can lie to him or temporize.


421
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:00,530
It will be better than


422
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,400
make him sad


423
00:30:05,910 --> 00:30:07,640
and bitterly disappointed day and night.


424
00:30:09,280 --> 00:30:11,200
I have feelings for His Majesty,


425
00:30:13,020 --> 00:30:14,800
but that’s not what he wants.


426
00:30:15,770 --> 00:30:17,640
If I lie to him or temporize,


427
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,510
pretending to love him very much,


428
00:30:21,420 --> 00:30:23,240
that will hurt him more.


429
00:30:23,910 --> 00:30:24,800
Just like you.


430
00:30:25,370 --> 00:30:27,370
If I ask you to pretend


431
00:30:29,110 --> 00:30:30,880
to be indifferent to His Majesty,


432
00:30:31,370 --> 00:30:32,530
can you do it?


433
00:30:36,530 --> 00:30:37,910
Why did you say so?


434
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:40,310
His Majesty is so distinguished


435
00:30:40,710 --> 00:30:42,620
that I can never think of that.


436
00:30:42,930 --> 00:30:43,820
Kuang Lu,


437
00:30:44,220 --> 00:30:45,370
take it easy.


438
00:30:45,910 --> 00:30:46,970
I don’t mean to blame you.


439
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:48,840
In fact,


440
00:30:50,130 --> 00:30:51,420
you and I are the same.


441
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:54,220
We both know in heart


442
00:30:54,570 --> 00:30:56,080
we can’t be with the ones we love,


443
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:00,530
but we can’t cheat our hearts.


444
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:03,770
I promise you.


445
00:31:04,170 --> 00:31:05,730
No one else


446
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:08,930
will know our conversations today.


447
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:10,660
Don’t worry.


448
00:31:12,750 --> 00:31:13,730
Thank you, Water Immortal.


449
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:15,860
I’ll be leaving.


450
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:26,970
Yesterday, I was injured
by the Light of Xuanqionge,


451
00:31:28,130 --> 00:31:29,550
but I am fine today.


452
00:31:29,910 --> 00:31:31,730
How can I recover so fast?


453
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:36,970
What is your color?


454
00:31:52,350 --> 00:31:53,110
Your Majesty.


455
00:31:53,860 --> 00:31:54,710
Has she woken up?


456
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:56,440
I told her that


457
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:59,110
Your Majesty was fine and
had gone to discuss matters with others,


458
00:31:59,820 --> 00:32:02,440
and would go to see her later.


459
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:12,000
Your Majesty,


460
00:32:12,930 --> 00:32:16,040
Blood Ball will consume half of your life.


461
00:32:16,660 --> 00:32:18,000
Is it worthy


462
00:32:18,530 --> 00:32:19,770
to do this?


463
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:25,370
Has Immortal Tai Si joined with Lord Po Jun?


464
00:32:27,910 --> 00:32:28,620
OK.


465
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:31,330
Tell him


466
00:32:31,820 --> 00:32:33,020
once the war begins,


467
00:32:34,040 --> 00:32:35,330
I will show up.


468
00:32:35,950 --> 00:32:36,800
Your Majesty,


469
00:32:37,370 --> 00:32:38,750
you are weak now


470
00:32:39,110 --> 00:32:40,310
and need rest.


471
00:32:40,970 --> 00:32:42,350
If you go to the battlefield now,


472
00:32:43,860 --> 00:32:44,880
it’ll be too dangerous.


473
00:32:45,770 --> 00:32:47,330
Since I took this position,


474
00:32:49,110 --> 00:32:50,710
I have to be responsible for Heaven Realm.


475
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:53,330
Your Majesty.


476
00:33:19,460 --> 00:33:20,750
Supreme Lord Lao.


477
00:33:24,570 --> 00:33:25,860
Water Immortal.


478
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:29,680
Yesterday, you almost died yesterday.


479
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:33,730
How can you recover so fast?


480
00:33:35,370 --> 00:33:36,530
I almost died?


481
00:33:37,330 --> 00:33:38,170
So serious?


482
00:33:39,060 --> 00:33:42,350
Do you have any elixir to cure me?


483
00:33:42,620 --> 00:33:43,600
Water Immortal,


484
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:45,550
I don’t have any elixir


485
00:33:45,820 --> 00:33:48,350
to heal the injury caused
by the Light of Xuanqiong.


486
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:51,640
Is there any other way?


487
00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:55,730
What do you think of?


488
00:33:56,260 --> 00:33:57,910
In ancient times,


489
00:33:57,910 --> 00:34:00,130
there was a book called Mengtuo Scripture


490
00:34:00,350 --> 00:34:02,170
in which all kinds of
forbidden magic are recorded.


491
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:04,970
I seem to hear of


492
00:34:05,770 --> 00:34:08,170
a kind of magic named Blood Ball


493
00:34:08,750 --> 00:34:10,219
which can change fate.


494
00:34:10,750 --> 00:34:11,679
But…


495
00:34:11,679 --> 00:34:12,710
But what?


496
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:16,880
According to the book,


497
00:34:17,330 --> 00:34:18,929
the rescuer needs to
cut seven sinews and vessels


498
00:34:19,770 --> 00:34:21,909
to inject half essence in his body


499
00:34:21,909 --> 00:34:23,510
into the blood


500
00:34:23,820 --> 00:34:25,150
to make Blood Ball


501
00:34:25,730 --> 00:34:26,620
to feed the injured.


502
00:34:27,150 --> 00:34:28,710
The rescuer


503
00:34:28,710 --> 00:34:32,570
will consume half of his life.


504
00:35:06,130 --> 00:35:06,620
Mi.


505
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:11,110
You seldom come to my room.


506
00:35:12,620 --> 00:35:13,770
What do you come here for?


507
00:35:23,240 --> 00:35:24,570
Have you ever heard of


508
00:35:25,420 --> 00:35:26,880
the magic Blood Ball?


509
00:35:27,550 --> 00:35:28,660
If you didn’t make Blood Ball,


510
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:30,660
how would you be injured,


511
00:35:32,310 --> 00:35:33,770
and how would I be safe?


512
00:35:36,310 --> 00:35:37,280
That’s not true.


513
00:35:37,910 --> 00:35:39,200
Where did you hear this?


514
00:35:40,130 --> 00:35:41,950
No one will use such
evil magic in Heaven Realm.


515
00:35:42,750 --> 00:35:44,040
You were not seriously injured yesterday.


516
00:35:44,750 --> 00:35:46,350
I just transferred some magic power to you.


517
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:48,350
OK.


518
00:35:48,710 --> 00:35:49,770
Since you don’t admit it,


519
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:52,170
I’m going to call Immortal Qihuang.


520
00:35:52,620 --> 00:35:53,150
Mi.


521
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:56,970
Are you insane?


522
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:58,530
Do you know


523
00:35:58,710 --> 00:36:00,710
you will consume half of your life by doing so?


524
00:36:01,020 --> 00:36:01,770
If you died,


525
00:36:02,530 --> 00:36:03,510
I would go insane.


526
00:36:05,770 --> 00:36:08,440
Blood Ball is the forbidden magic
recorded in Mengtuo Scripture.


527
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,350
There is Dream Changing Magic.


528
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:12,080
There is also Blood Ball.


529
00:36:12,970 --> 00:36:15,150
Did you never read Mengtuo Scripture?


530
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:16,880
Do you doubt


531
00:36:18,660 --> 00:36:19,950
I made you misunderstand Xu Feng?


532
00:36:21,460 --> 00:36:23,600
Even if there was someone playing a trick,


533
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:26,000
it must be the one


534
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,770
who killed your father.


535
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:34,880
Mi,


536
00:36:37,060 --> 00:36:38,350
I didn’t know Blood Ball


537
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:41,200
is also the forbidden magic
recorded in Mengtuo Scripture.


538
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:43,240
After my mother died,


539
00:36:43,910 --> 00:36:45,200
I brought some remains of hers


540
00:36:45,600 --> 00:36:47,330
to Heaven Realm from Dongting Lake.


541
00:36:47,770 --> 00:36:49,020
Blood Ball


542
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:51,600
is a kind of magic recorded by my mother.


543
00:36:52,620 --> 00:36:53,770
I didn’t know whether it was true.


544
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,510
You were in danger,


545
00:36:58,220 --> 00:36:59,640
so I had to have a try.


546
00:37:00,750 --> 00:37:01,910
Even if I died,


547
00:37:03,550 --> 00:37:05,200
it was a worthy death.


548
00:37:05,950 --> 00:37:08,840
Back then, Lord Puchi saved me,


549
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:12,530
and I paid him back with 1,000 years of magic power.


550
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:15,280
Now,


551
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:18,970
you have given me half of your life.


552
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,840
How can I pay you back?


553
00:37:23,020 --> 00:37:24,350
I don’t need that.


554
00:37:28,570 --> 00:37:29,510
Mi,


555
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:31,510
as long as I can watch you


556
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:34,040
and be at your side,


557
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:35,950
that is enough.


558
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:39,280
In the past, I had the whole night sky,


559
00:37:39,820 --> 00:37:41,550
but I still felt lonely.


560
00:37:43,330 --> 00:37:44,840
Now I have you,


561
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,860
so I feel content.


562
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:52,080
Mi,


563
00:37:53,110 --> 00:37:56,800
I only hope you can be carefree


564
00:37:57,280 --> 00:37:58,440
and happy as before.


565
00:38:00,620 --> 00:38:01,370
I hope


566
00:38:02,220 --> 00:38:03,820
you can be as happy as when I first met you.


567
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,280
Do you understand?


568
00:38:13,770 --> 00:38:14,620
Sorry.


569
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:16,840
I,


570
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:23,510
I love Xu Feng only.


571
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:26,170
I can’t forget him.


572
00:38:26,970 --> 00:38:28,710
I miss him so much.


573
00:38:30,130 --> 00:38:31,240
I miss him so much that


574
00:38:32,660 --> 00:38:35,420
every inch of my hair feels pain.


575
00:38:37,730 --> 00:38:38,620
I can’t forget him.


576
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:42,260
Don’t hurt yourself for me.


577
00:38:46,260 --> 00:38:47,280
Sorry.


578
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:56,000
If I also almost died like him one day,


579
00:38:59,110 --> 00:39:00,530
would you also risk your life to save me?


580
00:39:01,860 --> 00:39:02,710
Of course.


581
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:07,110
Because,


582
00:39:08,970 --> 00:39:10,350
that’s what I owe you.


